  "prompt": "How many seats are available in MA English in GGSIPU?",
  "response": "Guru Gobind Singh Indraprastha University (GGSIPU) offers MA English through its various affiliated colleges. The number of seats available for MA English can vary from year to year and depends on the specific college within GGSIPU.\n\nTypically, the total number of seats for MA English across all affiliated colleges might range from around 60 to 120 seats. However, for the most accurate and up-to-date information, I recommend checking the official GGSIPU website or contacting the university's admission office directly. They can provide the exact number of seats available for the current academic year and details about the application process.",
